data.description: Custom-built home with breathtaking views of Pikes Peak from all the west-facing windows and balconies displaying the ever changing daily portraits of the Rocky Mountains. This property offers 2 Master Suites each with enormous walk-in closets and private balconies. This home has all the upgrades you could want; fully xeriscape'd and maintenance-free AstroTurf, Beetle Kill Blue Pine Flooring throughout the main level and matching custom built Beetle Kill Blue Pine sliding Barn Door window coverings in the bedrooms carrying the color and wood style throughout the home, additional outdoor storage shed in matching color scheme, heated and air conditioned over-sized 2 car attached garage with its own wall-mounted TV (included) and automatic garage door opener, 360° video/voice surveillance system, thermostat controlled A/C and Forced Heat in the home, whole house humidifier, Heavy Duty Exterior Security Doors, Vinyl Crank Windows, Wood Burning Stove, Stainless Steel Appliances, and a Shatterproof Basketball Backboard & Rim Combo Hoop over the exterior garage door to top it all off. Every level of this home has outside patios with spectacular unobstructed views of the front range. The home is located within minutes of I-25, HWY 24 and Garden of the Gods. Centrally located in walking distance to Downtown Colorado Springs, Old Colorado City and just a short drive to the the eastern part of the Colorado Springs Powers Corridor, short commute to Fort Carson, Schriever AFB, the Air Force Academy and to all the attractions and events El Paso County has to offer.
